***HELP "RLC Model"***

***To create new system you have to write correct values 
of elements and switch them on using checkboxes, push play.
***To try example programs - choose option Load from MENU 
and select a system.
***To manage your systems use options:
Save as/Load from file located in MENU.
***To set the display of the screen of element's voltage
move the knobs under the screen.

OPEN SOURCE: https://github.com/K4liber/rlc

***THANK YOU FOR ATTENTION***